      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i have a question about my insulin. im type 1 and i usually take my basal dose in the evening but i barely ate anything for dinner tonight, like just a few bites of salad. do u think it's okay if i just skip my evening dose tonight so my blood sugar doesnt crash too low?",
